cz.kinst.jakub.diploma.udpbroadcast

Class UDPBroadcast

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.kinst.jakub.diploma.udpbroadcast.UDPBroadcast
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaUDPBroadcast

    public abstract class UDPBroadcast
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for the actual UDP communication. It is abstract because the implementation of some methods differ across the platforms (Java SE/Android). It represents the physical networking layer.

    It can broadcast the UDP packets via sendPacket(byte[]) method. It is also used to listen for incoming UDP broadcast packet. To do so, you have to call startReceiving() method.

    --------------------------- Created by Jakub Kinst 2014 E-mail: jakub@kinst.cz

        public final void sendPacket(byte[] packet)
